  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Kota is coming to Sri Lanka",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa will return to Sri Lanka in early September, according to government sources.",
        "Although it was announced earlier that he will return to Sri Lanka tomorrow (24), who is staying in Thailand, it is known that the said trip will be delayed by about two weeks.",
        "It can be understood that the reason for this delay is that discussions are taking place regarding the security of the former president and other issues.",
        "The intelligence agency has advised him to delay his return as security is a major issue.",
        "According to government sources, he may return in two weeks or earlier once his security arrangements are completed."
      ],
